name: WhichFlyShouldITry
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: trying flies
des: Fly fishing is a great way to stay active, and tying flies allows you to keep your mind sharp even when you're not out fishing! Staying sharp isn't just important for fish hooks! While everyone knows the Wooly B, this Alexa skill can inspire you with some other easy and effective flies to try tying.
